Disclaimer - using new driver on old OS might create hardware problem, so use it on ur own risk

Guide

move/remove catalog file from driver folder
like e2f68.cat

with notepad open the inf file and replace (Control+H)
10.0...17763
to
10.0.1

F8 before the OS loading
choose disable driver signature enforcement
and install the driver

Done


----------------


